"title": "8440: glorifying God",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8440",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The giving of glory to God through acts of praise and obedience. Believers are to glorify God in their lives, as Jesus Christ glorified him in his life.</p>\n<h2>Believers are to glorify God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps96:1-Ps96:9\">PSA 96:1–96:9</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:23-1Chr16:29\">1CH 16:23–16:29</a><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:12\">ISA 42:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa43:5-Isa43:7\">ISA 43:5–43:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa66:18-Isa66:19\">ISA 66:18–66:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:14\">HAB 2:14</a></p>\n<h3>God is entitled to be glorified</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps96:4-Ps96:9\">PSA 96:4–96:9</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:25-1Chr16:29\">1CH 16:25–16:29</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps29:1-Ps29:2\">PSA 29:1–29:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps115:1\">PSA 115:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa24:14-Isa24:15\">ISA 24:14–24:15</a></p>\n<h3>Glorifying God is the believer's natural response to him</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps118:28\">PSA 118:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps34:3\">PSA 34:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps69:30\">PSA 69:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps86:12\">PSA 86:12</a></p>\n<h2>God is glorified in Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:31\">JHN 13:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:13\">JHN 14:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:4\">JHN 17:4</a></p>\n<h2>Reasons for glorifying God</h2>\n<h3>His holiness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps99:9\">PSA 99:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev15:4\">REV 15:4</a></p>\n<h3>His great deeds</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps86:8-Ps86:10\">PSA 86:8–86:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa25:1\">ISA 25:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:13-2Cor4:15\">2CO 4:13–4:15</a></p>\n<h3>His loving mercy</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps63:3\">PSA 63:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps115:1\">PSA 115:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:8-Rom15:9\">ROM 15:8–15:9</a></p>\n<h3>His righteous judgments</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:7\">REV 14:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek28:22-Ezek28:23\">EZK 28:22–28:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:33-Rom11:36\">ROM 11:33–11:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev11:13\">REV 11:13</a></p>\n<h2>Means of glorifying God</h2>\n<h3>By praising God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev4:11\">REV 4:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev7:12\">REV 7:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:13\">LUK 2:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:33-Rom11:36\">ROM 11:33–11:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:27\">ROM 16:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:20-Heb13:21\">HEB 13:20–13:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:11\">1PE 4:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:18\">2PE 3:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:25\">JUD 1:25</a></p>\n<h3>By living for God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:31\">1CO 10:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom4:20\">ROM 4:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:20\">1CO 6:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:11-2Thess1:12\">2TH 1:11–1:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:10-1Pet4:13\">1PE 4:10–4:13</a></p>\n<h3>By doing good works and bearing fruit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:8\">JHN 15:8</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:9-Phil1:11\">PHP 1:9–1:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:16\">MAT 5:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:22-Gal5:26\">GAL 5:22–5:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:20-Heb13:21\">HEB 13:20–13:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:12\">1PE 2:12</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of glorifying God</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:10-1Chr29:13\">1CH 29:10–29:13</a> <em>David</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:34-Dan4:37\">DAN 4:34–4:37</a> <em>Nebuchadnezzar</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:46\">LUK 1:46</a> <em>Mary, the mother of Jesus Christ</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:13\">LUK 2:13</a> <em>the angels</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:20\">LUK 2:20</a> <em>the shepherds</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:31-John13:32\">JHN 13:31–13:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:1-John17:4\">JHN 17:1–17:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev4:11\">REV 4:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev7:12\">REV 7:12</a></p>",
